fields.name: CurrentCount
fields.description: A value that represents the number of properties used by the environment for S1/S2 SKU and number of properties used by Warm Store for PAYG SKU

fields.name: MaxCount
fields.description: A value that represents the maximum number of properties used allowed by the environment for S1/S2 SKU and maximum number of properties allowed by Warm Store for PAYG SKU.
